1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,000
Your body doesn't
know it's Saturday.

2
00:00:02,000 --> 00:00:06,000
You sleep until noon. You
feel great... until Monday.

3
00:00:06,000 --> 00:00:16,000
Your circadian clock runs on light and wake time. When you shift your schedule by
3 hours on Saturday, your body spends Sunday and Monday trying to catch up.

4
00:00:16,000 --> 00:00:24,000
The 90-minute rule: never wake more than 90 minutes
later than your weekday alarm. Even on vacation.

5
00:00:24,000 --> 00:00:30,000
Link in bio — free
energy profile in 30 seconds.

